♪ and nothing too new

963
01:48:31,964 --> 01:48:35,009
♪ Sing to the light of day

964
01:48:35,092 --> 01:48:36,844
♪ You'll smile for me,

965
01:48:36,928 --> 01:48:40,014
♪ we'll be happy that way

966
01:48:40,097 --> 01:48:50,983
♪ Da la la ...

967
01:48:51,067 --> 01:48:54,320
♪ Just turn away and

968
