♪ Sing to the light of day

985
01:49:49,834 --> 01:49:51,585
♪ You'll smile for me,

986
01:49:51,669 --> 01:49:54,714
♪ we'll be happy that way

987
01:49:54,797 --> 01:49:57,717
♪ And take this point of view

988
01:49:57,800 --> 01:49:59,552
♪ Nothing is old,

989
01:49:59,635 --> 01:50:02,513
♪ and nothing is new

